The '''Blue Mountain People''' were a tribe of [[Kwi]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]]. In [[23 ABY/Legends|23 ABY]], they were seen racing across the plains by [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Tenel Ka Djo|Tenel Ka]], during their trip to the planet onboard the ''[[Off Chance]].''<ref name="YJK:SA">''[[Young Jedi Knights: Shadow Academy]]''</ref>

